---
layout: blog
title: "Luxival Journal"
description: "Insights on software testing, agentic workflow design, and premium digital experiences from Helsinki."
permalink: "blog/index.html"
---
<span class="eyebrow">Blog</span>
<h1>Ideas for modern luxury, QA, and digital builds.</h1>
<p>Short, focused articles on software testing, agentic workflow strategy, and the craftsmanship behind Luxival's digital and travel services.</p>

<div class="gold-line" style="margin:3rem 0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold),transparent)"></div>

<div id="soro-blog"></div>

{% set posts = collections.blog | reverse %}
{% if posts.length %}
  <div class="blog-grid">
    {% for post in posts %}
      <article class="post-card">
        <div class="post-meta">{{ post.date | date("yyyy-MM-dd") }}</div>
        <h3 class="post-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a class="post-link" href="{{ post.url }}">Read post →</a>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
{% else %}
  <p>New posts are being prepared. Check back soon for updates.</p>
{% endif %}

<div style="margin-top:2.4rem;padding:1.2rem;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,106,.2);border-radius:6px;background:rgba(201,169,106,.04)">
  <span class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:.45rem">Next step</span>
  <p style="margin:0 0 .8rem;opacity:.75">Use the route that matches your current goal.</p>
  <div style="display:flex;gap:.6rem;flex-wrap:wrap">
    <a class="btn" href="/tourism#rideRequestForm" style="padding:.55rem .9rem;font-size:.72rem">Plan my Finland trip</a>
    <a href="/digital#consultation" style="border:1px solid var(--gold);padding:.55rem .9rem;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.72rem">Project consultation</a>
    <a href="/audit" style="border:1px solid var(--gold);padding:.55rem .9rem;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.72rem">Run free scan</a>
    <a href="/contact#newsletterForm" style="border:1px solid var(--gold);padding:.55rem .9rem;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:1.2px;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.72rem">Newsletter</a>
  </div>
</div>
